condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Section I.A.4. of Schedule 2 | Description :No later than one (1) month after the Effective Date, the Recipientshall establish, and thereafter maintain, throughout the implementation of the Project, a Project Steering Committee, which shallbeled by the MOF and shall include representatives from the MEE, MAI and MIOTH, with terms of reference, composition and resourcessatisfactory to the Association, as further defined in the PIM. | Due Date :14-Dec-2017

Finance Agreement :Section I.C.1. of Schedule 2 | Description :The Recipient shall update, not later than forty-five (45) daysafter the Effective Date, the Project Implementation Manual, in a manner satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :30-Oct-2017

Finance Agreement :Section V.1. of Schedule 2 of FA | Description :The Recipient shall, no later than six (6) months after theEffective Date, implement an axle load control, in a manner satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :14-May-2018

Finance Agreement :Section V.2. of Schedule 2 of FA | Description :No later than twelve (12) months after the Effective Date, theRecipient shall approve, and shall cause FAMR to adopt and thereafter implement, the recommendations of the study to increase theefficacy and efficiency of FAMR, which shall be undertaken under Part D(1) of the Project. | Due Date :14-Nov-2018
